- Update to version 1.8:
  * main.c: Added new option '-a, --trailing-error'.
  * main.c (decompress): Print up to 6 bytes of trailing data
    when '-vvvv' is specified.
  * decoder.c (LZd_verify_trailer): Removed test of final code.
